# ITBench: SRE and FinOps Applications

ITBench uses applications managed by open source communities as the subjects of benchmark. Faults are injected into the services, causing observable issues.

The following applications are already configured to work with the ITBench environment.

>[!NOTE]
>Many of these applications are demos or sample application built to showcase various capabilities. While stable, they are normally not production-level grade.

